reason.tex:
\begin{align}
A=\left[\begin{array}{cc}
3 & 2 \\ 7 & 1
\end{array}\right]
\end{align} \\
%text
Minor for each element,
%
\begin{align}
  M_{11}=1,\, M_{12}=7,\, M_{21}=2,\, M_{22}=3
\end{align} \\
%text
Therefore, Cofactor Matrix is,
%
\begin{align}
A=\left[\begin{array}{cc}
1(-1)^{1+1} & 7(-1)^{1+2} \\ 2(-1)^{2+1} & 3(-1)^{2+2}
\end{array}\right]=
\left[\begin{array}{cc}
1 & -7 \\ -2 & 3
\end{array}\right]
\end{align}
